Foundation Finance - Home Improvement Financing














































 














Foundation Finance CompanyFull service consumer financing for prime and subprime credit. 1-855-241-0024
FacebookTwitterYouTube





What Does Foundation Finance Offer?




At Foundation Finance Company (FFC), we know that access to consumer financing can make or break a sale. So we have developed flexible, competitive financing programs for prime, near-prime and subprime credit that help our dealers and contractors close more sales in less time with less hassle. With access to revolving or installment loans, same-as-cash, deferred payment and reduced interest rate promotions and credit approvals for most customers, you can close more sales and build your bottom line. 


 
