FacebookTwitterYouTube




You are here: Home / Program OverviewProgram Overview

 
 
 
 
Foundation Finance Program Overview
Unlike banks or traditional lenders, Foundation Finance has three approval tiers to be able to offer financing plans for customers with prime, near prime and subprime credit. Our loan programs have low, flexible payment options and you can also offer your customer an attractive promotion to help close the sale. The process is quick and easy and you can have a credit decision in minutes!
Foundation Finance offers several tools for you to build on in addition to training resources to help make your entire office successful at offering financing!
Don’t wait any longer, becoming a dealer is FREE and EASY! Request your free signup kit and enroll today!
