Loan Programs - Foundation Finance Company















































 














Foundation Finance CompanyFull service consumer financing for prime and subprime credit. 1-855-241-0024
FacebookTwitterYouTube




You are here: Home / Program Overview / Loan ProgramsLoan Programs
We offer a variety of loan programs to meet your customers’ needs.
Revolving lines of credit*

Low 2% monthly payment factor (on a $3000 loan, that’s only $60/month). Tier 1 and Tier 2 bids for home improvement contractors and water treatment dealers are eligible for a 1.5% reduced payment factor.
Simple repeat sales at your business

*Ask about availability.
Installment loans

Fixed payments and terms give customers peace of mind
Terms up to 120 months

Full service credit programs
At Foundation Finance we offer a full service consumer financing program for prime, near prime and subprime customers. See our page on credit approval tiers for more information.
For your less than perfect credit customers, rather than decline them, we may off you a discounted bid.  Click here to learn more about discount financing.
We also offer a variety of promotions to help you close more sales!
